appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What's new:

Effect controls have a new look. Effects and their parameter should be easier to organize.

Also, quite a few new effects were added!
Look out for:
Emojis! Choose from over 20 different emojis to overlay on your detected props.
Kaleidoscope! This effect has several new parameters. Try it out!
Particles! Decorate your flow with particles with customizable physics! You can customize motion, gravity, and the density of particles rendered.

creator: ian borukhovich
descriptionHtml:
Check www.instagram.com/arflowarts for examples and tutorials :)

Transform your flow arts, dance and movement videos with endless possibilities. Make your props change colors, add trails to your body, pour fairy dust from your flow, connect your juggling with webs of lines and much much more. The basic effects are free forever!!!
descriptionShort: Video Effects Made for Flow Arts, Dance and Movement!
